(6411, 213, '<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;Array (larik) bukanlah tipe data dasar seperti integer atau boolen. Array adalah sebuah tipe data bentukan yang terdiri atas kumpulan tipe data lainnya. Menggunakan array akan memudahkan dalam membuat kelompok data, serta menghemat penulisan dan penggunaan variabel. Berikut yang merupakan cara pendeklarasian array pada PHP adalah ....</p>\r\n', 1, '', '<p>&lt;?php<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$nama = array (<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;0 =&gt; &quot;HTML&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1 =&gt; &quot;CSS&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2 =&gt; &quot;JavaScript&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3 =&gt; &quot;PHP&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4 =&gt; &quot;MySQL&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;?&gt;</p>\r\n', '<p>&lt;?php<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$nama = array (<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[0] = &quot;HTML&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[1] = &quot;CSS&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[2] = &quot;JavaScript&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[3] = &quot;PHP&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[4] = &quot;MySQL&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;?&gt;</p>\r\n', '<p>&lt;?php<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$nama = array (<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[1] = &quot;HTML&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[2] = &quot;CSS&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[3] = &quot;JavaScript&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[4] = &quot;PHP&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;[5] = &quot;MySQL&quot;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;?&gt;</p>\r\n', '<p>&lt;?php<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$nama = array (<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1 =&gt; &quot;HTML&quot;,&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2 =&gt; &quot;CSS&quot;,&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3 =&gt; &quot;JavaScript&quot;,&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4 =&gt; &quot;PHP&quot;,<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5 =&gt; &quot;MySQL&quot;) ;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;?&gt;</p>\r\n', '<p>&lt;?php<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$nama = array (<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;0 = &